		<p>
			<lb n="1"/><gap quantity="2" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap><unclear>kan</unclear> para<unclear>m</unclear>pu <unclear>na</unclear> nilamā
			<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭaiyān mātavan parama–
			<lb n="3"/>Arai paṭṭan tiruvai–
			<lb n="4" break="no"/>yan kaṟaikkaṇṭana ni–
			<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷḷān Irā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<supplied reason="omitted"><hi rend="grantha">ja</hi></supplied>n nila–
			<lb n="6" break="no"/><gap quantity="1" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap>ḍeva coṟuṭaiyā–
			<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṭukku Ivai e–
	
			
		</p>
		
		
		
